module TopModule (
    input logic clk,
    input logic j,
    input logic k,
    output logic Q
);
    always @(posedge clk) begin
        case ({j, k})
            2'b00: Q <= Q;       // Qold
            2'b01: Q <= 1'b0;    // 0
            2'b10: Q <= 1'b1;    // 1
            2'b11: Q <= ~Q;      // ~Qold
        endcase
    end
endmodule
